{
  "texts": [
    "It can express persistent misconceptions about a topic (based on its training data).",
    "AI may have a shallow grasp of a concept and may not easily be able to provide clear explanations, examples, or analogies.",
    "Additionally, it can be fickle and refuse to perform actions it is capable of performing and it can get stuck in a loop.",
    "There are techniques instructors can use to mitigate these issues and we have used many of these techniques in the prompts.",
    "For instance, we include context to provide the AI with specific domain knowledge to draw on, give the AI examples, and we provide the AI with step-by-step directions."
  ]
}